		"excerpt": "CloudFlare is a Crunchie finalist in the category for Best Cloud Service in 2011. We need your help and your vote to win the category! The Crunchies are supported by VentureBeat, TechCrunch and GigaOm. ",
		"feature_image": "https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/5Tvo8VrMm5QvcutrKrnXqv/7cfba0c3c42dc52a8032ba110116792c/cloudflare-has-been-nominated-for-a-crunchie.gif",
		"featured": false,
		"html": "<p></p><p>CloudFlare is a Crunchie finalist in the category for Best Cloud Service in 2011. We need your help and <a href=\"http://crunchies2011.techcrunch.com/vote/?OTo0OQ==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">your vote</a> to win the category! The Crunchies are supported by <a href=\"http://venturebeat.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">VentureBeat</a>, <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TechCrunch</a> and <a href=\"http://gigaom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GigaOm</a>. Over 300,000 nominations came in from 20 different countries, but the contest isn&#39;t over yet. We need your help in becoming the Best Cloud Service in 2011!</p><p>Everyone is invited to vote once per category per day until Sunday, January 29, 2012 at 11:59pm PST. Click below to cast your vote for CloudFlare.</p><p>[</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/6IfBdKMqvvLIIgaVN0d2Mz/66e649ac0aba0449d2f3f4ec81d325d4/crunchies_2011_wide.png.scaled500.png\" alt=\"CloudFlare Has Been Nominated for a Crunchie!\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"160\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>](<a href=\"http://crunchies2011.techcrunch.com/vote/?OTo0OQ==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://crunchies2011.techcrunch.com/vote/?OTo0OQ==</a>)</p><p>Finalists will be announced January 31, 2012 in San Francisco. Don&#39;t forget to <a href=\"http://crunchies2011.techcrunch.com/vote/?OTo0OQ==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">vote for CloudFlare</a>!</p>",
		"id": "4WJyLNwwqQAgnRUpjRWQq0",
